n class=\"font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-ctp-subtext0\">GIT REPOS</span></div></div></div></section></div><section id=\"about\" class=\"relative border border-ctp-surface1/70 bg-ctp-mantle/70 backdrop-blur \"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"pointer-events-none absolute h-3 w-3 border-hud/80 left-[-1px] top-[-1px] border-l-2 border-t-2\"></span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"pointer-events-none absolute h-3 w-3 border-hud/80 right-[-1px] top-[-1px] border-r-2 border-t-2\"></span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"pointer-events-none absolute h-3 w-3 border-hud/80 bottom-[-1px] left-[-1px] border-b-2 border-l-2\"></span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"pointer-events-none absolute h-3 w-3 border-hud/80 bottom-[-1px] right-[-1px] border-b-2 border-r-2\"></span><header class=\"flex items-center justify-between gap-4 border-b border-ctp-surface1/60 px-4 py-2.5 sm:px-6\"><h2 class=\"font-mono text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-hud hud-glow sm:text-sm\">CREW MANIFEST — PIC PROFILE</h2><div class=\"shrink-0 font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-ctp-overlay0\">REC 001/001</div></header><div class=\"p-4 sm:p-6 \"><div class=\"grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-[220px,1fr]\"><div class=\"mx-auto md:mx-0\"><div class=\"relative\"><img src=\"/imgs/about-pic.png\" alt=\"Abdihamid Moallim\" class=\"h-52 w-52 border border-ctp-surface1 object-cover\"/><span class=\"absolute -bottom-px -right-px h-3 w-3 border-b-2 border-r-2 border-hud\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span><span class=\"absolute -left-px -top-px h-3 w-3 border-l-2 border-t-2 border-hud\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span></div><dl class=\"mt-3 space-y-1 font-mono text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.15em] text-ctp-subtext0\"><div class=\"flex justify-between gap-2\"><dt class=\"text-ctp-overlay0\">CALLSIGN</dt><dd class=\"text-hud\">ABMOALLIM</dd></div><div class=\"flex justify-between gap-2\"><dt class=\"text-ctp-overlay0\">ROLE</dt><dd>SOFTWARE ENGINEER</dd></div><div class=\"flex justify-between gap-2\"><dt class=\"text-ctp-overlay0\">STATUS</dt><dd class=\"text-hud\">ACTIVE</dd></div></dl></div><div class=\"space-y-5\"><div class=\"space-y-4 text-sm leading-relaxed text-ctp-subtext1 sm:text-base\"><p>I&#x27;m a Software Engineer with a passion for web technologies and AI, currently charting a course toward the aviation industry. Like a pilot navigating through complex airspace, I navigate through code with precision and purpose.</p><p>My journey in software development is driven by curiosity and innovation. Whether I&#x27;m building web applications or dreaming of cockpit displays, I approach every challenge with the same attention to detail that aviation demands.<!-- --> <span class=\"font-semibold text-hud\">Insha Allah</span>, I&#x27;ll soon be combining my technical skills with my aviation aspirations.</p></div><div><div class=\"mb-2 font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-ctp-overlay0\">CORE COMPETENCIES</div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 gap-2 min-[420px]:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 border border-ctp-surface1/70 bg-ctp-crust/50 px-3 py-2 font-mono text-xs text-ctp-subtext1\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-code h-3.5 w-3.5 shrink-0 text-ctp-sapphire\"><polyline points=\"16 18 22 12 16 6\"></polyline><polyline points=\"8 6 2 12 8 18\"></polyline></svg>Web Development</div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 border border-ctp-surface1/70 bg-ctp-crust/50 px-3 py-2 font-mono text-xs text-ctp-subtext1\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-brain h-3.5 w-3.5 shrink-0 text-ctp-mauve\"><path d=\"M12 5a3 3 0 1 0-5.997.